poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222210/extras/5ceb235332cd0a2f3989a03333a47f36.poster.avif?t=1745290483\" width=700 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222210/extras/5ceb235332cd0a2f3989a03333a47f36.webm?t=1745290483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222210/extras/5ceb235332cd0a2f3989a03333a47f36.mp4?t=1745290483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Have a fun victory!<br><br>* Thank you for supporting our Early Access version! Rest assured that we will keep updating, fixing, and adding more content like new campaign levels, units, and some more interesting gameplay mechanics.",
